        <header>
            
                <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review comment_btn "
                    data-isverify="False"
                    data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=http://movie.douban.com/subject/4300525/new_review">
                    <span>我要写影评</span>
                </a>
            <h2>
                    待业青年的影评 · · · · · ·

                    <span class="pl">( <a href="reviews">全部 388 条</a> )</span>
